Output demo.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1200
Set Height 550
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20
Set BorderRadius 8
Set WindowBar "Colorful"
Set TypingSpeed 75ms

Hide
Type "export PATH=/home/kunjee/Workspace/irona/target/release:$PATH"
Enter
Type "clear"
Enter
Show

Type "irona /tmp/irona-demo"
Enter
Wait /items found/

Sleep 800ms
Down
Sleep 400ms
Space
Sleep 400ms
Down
Sleep 400ms
Space
Sleep 600ms

Type "d"
Sleep 800ms
Type "y"
Sleep 3000ms
Type "q"
Sleep 500ms
